OL,4,G2100FArt's Wildest Movement: Mannerism
OL,5,     GThe Great Escape: The Sack of
OL,6,     GRome in 1527 forced many Italian
OL,7,     Gartists to flee abroad, taking
OL,8,     Gthe revolutionary art movement
OL,9,     Gwith them.
OL,10,G2200FWelcome to the Eighties
OL,11,     GLike the Beatles before them,
OL,12,     Gbands like Duran Duran and
OL,13,     GCulture Club now inspire rock's
OL,14,     Ghomeland, fueled by the rise of
OL,15,     GMTV. With flashing images.
OL,16,G2315FBoy George & Culture Club
OL,17,     GCulture Club emerged in the 80s
OL,18,     GUK new romantic scene with iconic
OL,19,     Gstyle and music. Explore their
OL,20,     Gjourney and influence,
OL,21,     Ghighlighting the unexpected
OL,22,     Gromance within the band. 2025.
